                    "comments": [
                        {
                            "type": {
                                "id": 201,
                                "en": "On-site releases comment",
                                "fr": "Commentaire sur les rejets sur le site"
                            },
                            "comment": "The reduction in nitrogen oxide (NOx) emissions in 2024 is primarily attributed to a decrease in electricity production levels. This reduction reflects our responsive operating strategy, where the facility adjusts generation based on prevailing market prices and system conditions. As market signals were less favourable for peaking generation during portions of the year, the facility operated fewer hours, resulting in lower overall emissions."
                        }
                    ],
