                                "fr": "Commentaire sur les rejets sur le site"
                            },
                            "comment": "The decrease in carbon monoxide (CO) emissions in 2024 is directly related to reduced electricity production at the facility. Northstone Power operates as a merchant generator and adjusts output in response to Alberta electricity market conditions. In 2024, fewer economically favourable dispatch opportunities led to lower operating hours, which in turn resulted in reduced CO emissions."
                        }
                    ],
